{"questionId":"13208","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The random variable <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"X\">\n  <mi>X</mi>\n</math></span> has probability density function <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n</math></span> given by</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage mjpage__block\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\left\\{ {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {k\\left( {\\pi - {\\text{arcsin}}\\,x} \\right)}&amp;{0 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 1} \\\\   0&amp;{{\\text{otherwise}}}  \\end{array}} \\right.,\\,\\,{\\text{where }}k{\\text{ is a positive constant}}{\\text{.}}\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>{</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mi>k</mi>\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mi>π</mi>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mtext>arcsin</mtext>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n                  <mi>x</mi>\n                </mrow>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>0</mn>\n              <mo>⩽</mo>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mo>⩽</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow>\n                <mtext>otherwise</mtext>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo fence=\"true